src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2322226c72baebe6827b2c78df61a9c7801dc86","tid":1660758,"uid":110113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T01:22:18.000Z","msg":"有思覺失調既係個老母"},{"pid":"4091111b4910446e49c8ef69da7fddc6b7470af6","tid":1660758,"uid":103363,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:14:49.000Z","msg":"只能夠話佢個藍絲老母係要佢個女死得不明不白冇辦法<br />\n一係根本冇乜溝通所以連個女嘅真實諗法都唔知仲戇鳩鳩以為又係收錢做野乜乜柒柒嗰D 社會垃圾<br />\n一係就係幫埋中共港共黑警屈死自己個女<br />\n兩邊都係應該死左去"},{"pid":"60d66403b32b846cd985dbf77d59df9e21c0f571","tid":1660758,"uid":54633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會係佢老母個黑警男友同佢嘈交，錯手殺死咗人，依家想護住個死黑警"},{"pid":"85f2e6e66b9cc3914556f3c3dac9efe63beba095","tid":1660758,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"60d66403b32b846cd985dbf77d59df9e21c0f571","tid":1660758,"uid":54633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:16:43.000Z","msg":"會唔會係佢老母個黑警男友同佢嘈交，錯手殺死咗人，依家想護住個死黑警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:18:36.000Z","msg":"有機會"},{"pid":"0c7921ce504befabdacaffcb7110aaa8355dd14d","tid":1660758,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:21:31.000Z","msg":"仲話無可疑"},{"pid":"8e2e3c1368e0efa2e37b11108f1dc2911626b469","tid":1660758,"uid":202898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-18T02:28:44.000Z","msg":"個老母真係好撚垃圾 15歲有同事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁細個就唔撚養逼住個女要出去做野<br />\n死臭閪Hello Kitty<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}